column22: Choose one —; • Agate Assault deals 4 damage to target creature. If that creature would die this turn, exile it instead.; • Exile target artifact.
When Bakersbane Duo enters, create a Food token.; Whenever you expend 4, Bakersbane Duo gets +1/+1 until end of turn. (You expend 4 as you spend your fourth total mana to cast spells during a turn.)

Gift a Treasure (You may promise an opponent a gift as you cast this spell. If you do, they create a Treasure token before its other effects. It's an artifact with "{T}, Sacrifice this artifact: Add one mana of any color."); Blooming Blast deals 2 damage to target creature. If the gift was promised, Blooming Blast also deals 3 damage to that creature's controller.
